        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi> [2d ed.].</p>  
<p>Does not feel his abstract of <hi rend="italic">Cross and self-fertilisation</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Am. J. Sci.</hi> 3d ser. 13 (1877): 125–41] was thorough enough.</p> 
            <p>Has heard of their sad bereavement last autumn [death of Amy, wife of Francis Darwin].</p>
